analyze_optimization.output_format:
Your output should be an Optimization Analysis Report (OR) with the following structure:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "document_type": "OR",
  "document": {
    "title": "Optimization Analysis Report",
    "summary": "Brief summary of optimization analysis",
    "performance_requirements": [
      {
        "id": "PR-001",
        "category": "Category (e.g., response time, throughput, resource usage)",
        "description": "Requirement description",
        "target_metric": "Specific measurable target",
        "criticality": "high/medium/low",
        "source": "Document reference"
      }
    ],
    "system_constraints": [
      {
        "id": "SC-001",
        "category": "Category (e.g., hardware, budget, time)",
        "description": "Constraint description",
        "impact": "Impact on performance optimization",
        "source": "Document reference"
      }
    ],
    "optimization_strategies": [
      {
        "id": "OS-001",
        "title": "Strategy title",
        "description": "Detailed description of the optimization strategy",
        "target_areas": ["Components or processes targeted"],
        "expected_benefits": "Expected improvements in performance",
        "implementation_complexity": "high/medium/low",
        "priority": "high/medium/low",
        "trade_offs": "Any trade-offs or downsides to consider",
        "measurement_approach": "How to measure the effectiveness of this strategy"
      }
    ],
    "llm_optimization": {
      "prompt_optimization": ["Strategies for optimizing prompts"],
      "context_management": ["Strategies for optimizing context usage"],
      "caching_strategies": ["Strategies for implementing caching"],
      "batching_approaches": ["Approaches for request batching"],
      "model_selection": ["Guidance on model selection for different tasks"]
    },
    "cost_optimization": {
      "estimated_costs": "Estimated operational costs",
      "cost_reduction_strategies": ["Strategies to reduce costs"],
      "roi_analysis": "Return on investment analysis for optimization efforts"
    },
    "implementation_roadmap": {
      "phases": [
        {
          "phase": "Phase name",
          "strategies": ["OS-001", "OS-003"],
          "estimated_effort": "Effort estimate",
          "expected_outcomes": "Expected outcomes from this phase"
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
```

examples.output:
{
  "status": "success",
  "document_type": "OR",
  "document": {
    "title": "Optimization Analysis Report: E-Commerce Platform",
    "summary": "This report analyzes performance requirements and provides optimization strategies for a high-traffic e-commerce platform, focusing on response time, throughput, and cost efficiency.",
    "performance_requirements": [
      {
        "id": "PR-001",
        "category": "response time",
        "description": "Product page load time must be minimal to reduce bounce rates",
        "target_metric": "< 1 second for 95th percentile of requests",
        "criticality": "high",
        "source": "Performance Constraints Document, p.3"
      },
      {
        "id": "PR-002",
        "category": "throughput",
        "description": "System must handle peak load during sales events",
        "target_metric": "Support 10,000 concurrent users with < 2s response time",
        "criticality": "high",
        "source": "System Requirements Document, p.7"
      }
    ],
    "optimization_strategies": [
      {
        "id": "OS-001",
        "title": "Implement CDN for static assets",
